trans-unit.source: Preprocesses keyboard or input messages within the message loop before they are dispatched.
trans-unit.target: 预处理键盘或输入的消息在消息循环内之前被发送。

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Message"></xref>, passed by reference, that represents the message to process.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Message"> </xref>，按引用传递，表示要处理的消息。

trans-unit.source: The possible values are WM_KEYDOWN, WM_SYSKEYDOWN, WM_CHAR, and WM_SYSCHAR.
trans-unit.target: 可能的值为 WM_KEYDOWN、 WM_SYSKEYDOWN、 WM_CHAR 和 WM_SYSCHAR。

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the message was processed by the control; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>如果消息已由控件; 处理否则为<xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>。

trans-unit.source: Processes a dialog key if the WebBrowser ActiveX control does not process it.
trans-unit.target: 如果 WebBrowser ActiveX 控件不会处理它，请处理对话框键。

trans-unit.source: This method is called during message preprocessing to handle dialog characters, such as TAB, RETURN, ESCAPE, and arrow keys.
trans-unit.target: 消息以处理对话框字符，例如选项卡、 返回、 转义符，和箭头键在预处理期间调用此方法。

trans-unit.source: This method is called only if the WebBrowser ActiveX control does not process the key.
trans-unit.target: 仅当 WebBrowser ActiveX 控件不会处理密钥，调用此方法。

trans-unit.source: In this case, this method delegates the call to the base <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.ProcessDialogKey%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method.
trans-unit.target: 在这种情况下，此方法将调用委托给基<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.ProcessDialogKey%2A?displayProperty=fullName>方法。</xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.ProcessDialogKey%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: One of the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Keys"></xref> values that represents the key to process.
trans-unit.target: 之一<xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Keys"></xref>这些值表示要处理的键。

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the key was processed by the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowserBase"></xref>; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>如果键已由处理<xref href="System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowserBase"> </xref>; 否则为<xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>。

trans-unit.source: Processes a mnemonic character.

trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>如果字符已由控件; 处理作为助记键否则为<xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>。
